Name: Eggroll
About the game: Roll the egg back into the nest in record time... without cracking! Eggroll is a 2D platformer featuring amusing physics, original art on every level, and randomly generated jazz music! Players control an egg, which can roll and jump - and crack! 24 levels to unlock each with a different theme 9 different player characters to unlock Jazz generator makes endless variations of jazz music
